After the campaign there's an awkward gap between that and the boss "rifts" - a boring grind to level 80. When you do get to 80, you get one shot by uber bosses.

Settings feature needs more options like control set-up, graphics level. Damage indicators should be specific, no clear color designation for character's damage, monster's damage, heal values, and crit numbers. Add interaction with environment. Promising game but needs polishing.
